entry.title: 150W LED Canopy Light, 5700K, 19000 Lumens, AC100-277V, DLC Premium, 525W HPS/HID Replacement, LED Gas Station Lighting
entry.summary:

Type: LED Canopy
Price: 261.20

Canopy Lights come in a slim and sleek design with a 5700K color temperature giving you bright day-white light for your property. Save up to 75% on utility bills with LED lights and get peace of mind for your investment with a 5-year limited manufacturer’s warranty.
